Invocation Name: rocket launcher
des:
Rocket Launcher helps to create a sequence of backward counting to indicate time remaining before the start of the event, starting from 100 to 0.
It can be used by parents or anyone on schedule to count down from 100 (or any other positive number less than 100) to zero.
For example, users can say "Alexa, ask Rocket Launcher start from 30" or "Alexa, ask Rocket Launcher launch for 60" or "Alexa, ask Rocket Launcher for two"

For any questions or feedback, please send a note to alexa@nectarspot.com
